    FigmaLocal & FigmaPlugin & FigmaRest --> Gate
    JiraRest & JiraPaste --> Gate
    CustomText & CustomStructured --> Gate

    Gate -->|"gate passes"| Envelope
    Gate -->|"gate fails"| GateFail["MultiSourceModeGateError\n(fail-closed, no artifacts)"]

    Envelope -->|"ok: true"| IRBuilders
    Envelope -->|"ok: false"| EnvFail["ValidationIssue[]\n(fail-closed, no artifacts)"]

    FigmaLocal & FigmaPlugin & FigmaRest --> FigmaIR
    JiraRest & JiraPaste --> JiraIR
    CustomText & CustomStructured --> CustomContextIR

    FigmaIR & JiraIR & CustomContextIR --> Reconciliation

    Reconciliation --> PIIRedact
    PIIRedact --> PromptCompiler
    PromptCompiler --> LLMGateway
    LLMGateway --> Validation
    Validation --> PolicyGate
    PolicyGate --> ReviewGate
    ReviewGate -->|"all approved"| ExportPipeline
    ExportPipeline --> EvidenceManifest

    FigmaRest -.->|"optional"| VisualClient
    VisualClient -.->|"sidecar result"| PolicyGate

